Class TheObject.Measurement

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.TheObject.Measurement
  • Enclosing class:
    TheObject

    static class TheObject.Measurement
extends java.lang.Object
    A (static) inner class for measurement jobs. The class records specific values of the object during the simulation. These values can be used for statistic evaluation.
